ping-continuous's purpose is to collect and display information about host availability.
This is alpha version, please check program for correctness.
It will be refactored heavily when I will have time.

It's a Perl modules/apps bundle.
Ping2DB.pm is a module to continuously ping a host and store result in DB
ping_graph.cgi is an utility to draw a graph based on collected data
collect.pl - utlity to collect data
